      <section eId="sec_5531">
        <num>5531</num>
        <heading>Description of action</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_5531__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>whether the appeal is on a full record, printed or reproduced, or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_5531__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>on the original record, in which event, state whether the appendix\nmethod is being used, or leave to prosecute the appeal on the original\nrecord was granted by the court or by statute.\n  The statement shall be prefixed to the papers constituting the record\non appeal. A copy of this statement shall be filed with the clerk at the\ntime the record on appeal is filed.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
